es, Concentrates and Metals of the Polish Committee for Standardization), Polskie Stowarzyszenie Pomiarów, Automatyki i Robotyki POLSPAR - komitet: Termografia i Termometria w Podczerwieni (Polish Association of Measurements, Automation and robotics POLSPAr - committee: Infrared Thermography and Thermometry).
